remote-control
==============

This product includes software developed as a derivative work based on
RustDesk, an open-source remote desktop software.

    RustDesk
    https://github.com/rustdesk/rustdesk
    Copyright (c) 2020 Purslane Ltd.
    Licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 (AGPL-3.0).

The unmodified RustDesk source code is imported via `git subtree` under
`client/upstream/` at a pinned upstream tag. A summary of modifications
made in this repository is maintained in `CHANGES.md`.

Bundled server components
-------------------------

The server stack distributes container images published by third parties:

    lejianwen/rustdesk-server
    https://github.com/lejianwen/rustdesk-server
    Licensed under AGPL-3.0.

    lejianwen/rustdesk-api
    https://github.com/lejianwen/rustdesk-api
    Licensed under AGPL-3.0.

These images are pulled at runtime by Docker Compose and are not modified.

